snippet.title: RanbooVODS
snippet.description:
This is a fan channel, an archive of Ranboo's VODs so they dont get lost due to twitch only keeping VODS for 60 days. 

Extra info about this channel:
https://twitter.com/ranaltboo/status/1428478338239279105
https://youtu.be/bdPM_DKjL04?t=5042 (He re-purposed the VOD's channel and made the above tweet)
